text: Your Auntie Edie's coming in for a cup of tea later and you know how she has a good look round everywhere. There was a tinkle and a thud from beside the coat cupboard. Cecil's mother turned around in time to see the briefcase collapse against the brass umbrella stand. 'Well now!' She hurried.
